        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利列為首選股後Intuit股價上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Intuit股價週四開盤後大幅上漲,此前摩根士丹利將該股票提升至其首選股名單,分析師Keith Weiss稱其為「折讓價格的持久複合增長股」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在報告中,摩根士丹利透露「我們將Intuit列為首選股,因為其估值在20倍GAAP市盈率下顯得極具吸引力」,並補充稱兩大產品週期支撐「營收加速增長的路徑」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Weiss認為,此次升級反映了具吸引力的進場點、近期催化劑以及長期增長潛力的結合。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-50497b7a-3da6-3169-b5a9-3134a4052b2e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他寫道,Intuit的估值「在增長調整基礎上看起來更具吸引力」,該股以「2026日曆年1.01倍PEG交易,而大型股同業平均為1.21倍,整體市場則超過1.6倍」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行還強調了Intuit第二財季業績後的全面強勁表現,包括「總營收增長17%,全球業務解決方案增長18%,線上生態系統增長21%,QBO Advanced和Intuit Enterprise Suite增長約40%」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Weiss表示,這些業績增強了對兩大關鍵產品週期(輔助報稅和中端市場會計與服務)的信心,他認為這些可以幫助Intuit「隨著時間推移回到20%的增長軌道」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示,輔助報稅業務的勢頭顯著,TurboTax「增長12%,儘管美國國稅局申報量較去年同期低5個百分點」,截至2月6日客戶訪問量已超過500萬。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利表示,4月季度第三財季業績是下一個重大催化劑,將提供「TurboTax增長持久性的更多明確性」以及2026財年預估上調的可能性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E5%88%97%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%82%A1%E5%BE%8Cintuit%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-171813265.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 01:26:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國家庭淨資產增加2.2萬億美元 升至紀錄新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著年末股市持續上漲，美國家庭財富第四季度升至紀錄新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會周四公佈的報告顯示，家庭淨資產較前一季度增加2.2萬億美元，達到184.1萬億美元。其中，美國家庭持有的股票資產價值增加1.6萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500指數第四季度延續漲勢並創紀錄，提振投資者財富。市場對人工智能以及企業盈利前景的樂觀情緒推動股價上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告還顯示，家庭持有的房地產資產價值減少約3470億美元，反映房地產市場表現疲軟。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f3062a27-dce2-31ab-a71b-854c4847ddaf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，消費者借貸以折年率3.3%的速度成長，為2025年第一季度以來最慢。非按揭消費者信貸成長加快，而按揭貸款增速明顯放緩。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業債務餘額以折年率2.4%的速度成長，為一年來最慢。在公共部門方面，州和地方政府債務幾無成長，而聯邦政府借款增速強勁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括儲蓄賬戶、支票賬戶和貨幣市場基金在內，家庭和非營利組織持有的存款成長3.3%，升至紀錄新高20.5萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Household Net Worth Climbs $2.2 Trillion to Fresh Record (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jarrell Dillard.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%B7%A8%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A02-2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-164524973.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 01:16:04",
