        {
            "title": "美銀:純多頭基金正在買入非美國股票",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據美國銀行的最新報告,純多頭投資者在2月份果斷轉向非美國股票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">量化策略師Nigel Tupper寫道,\"全球純多頭基金買入非美國股票,但賣出美國股票\",這標誌著區域配置出現明顯分化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀指出,主動型和被動型基金合計對新興市場的流入資金最多,購買了超過176億美元,其次是亞太地區,流入資金超過149億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下,最大的資金流出發生在美國,基金賣出了695億美元的股票。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ae2bc27c-d619-3b02-bd05-08e78725d63c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按板塊劃分,買入力度最強的是必需消費品板塊,超過79億美元,以及原材料板塊,超過50億美元,而軟件和媒體板塊則遭遇大量拋售,分別為177億美元和110億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告稱,上個月全球最大的純多頭股票買入包括沃爾瑪、艾伯維、羅氏和ASML,而主要賣出則包括阿斯利康、微軟、蘋果和輝達。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀強調,純多頭基金在全球持有最廣泛的股票仍然是台積電,擁有權比例為92%,其次是ARM,為88%,<span><span><span><span>微軟</span></span></span></span>為84%,<span><span>輝達</span></span>為74%,騰訊為72%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行還表示,\"擁擠的正面股票\"(即結合高擁有權和正面\"三重動能\"的股票)繼續跑贏大盤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些股票目前包括博通、台積電、三星電子、美光科技、SK海力士和禮來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80-%E7%B4%94%E5%A4%9A%E9%A0%AD%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E9%9D%9E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8-160907283.html",
